<http://www.spektrix.com/yukonartscentre/event/69201ARPJLTNJBTLLMTLRNMQHNSVKNBHM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Moppets Childrens Festival: Murphy and the Cats - Music for the Whole Family";
  schema:description """
	Murphy and the Cats are award winning young musicians who have been performing together since they were wee lads in elementary school.  On fiddle, drums and percussion, ukulele, guitar, double bass, kazoo and even a paper bag, the Cats know how to keep the audience entertained. Their repertoire is rooted in the popular music of the 20’s and 30’s and they will era hop into Beatles music and beyond to get your toes tapping. So put your dance shoes on and come out for a joyously good time! 
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-06T13:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
