	<h1>Yukon Theatre for Young People Presents: The Wizard of Oz</h1><span class=\"ItalicText\">Yukon Theatre for Young People is pleased to present this incredible production featuring a cast of Yukon young people ages 11-18.</span><span><br/></span>Follow the yellow brick road in this delightful stage adaptation of L. Frank Baum’s beloved tale, featuring the iconic musical score from the MGM film. The timeless tale, in which young Dorothy Gale travels from Kansas over the rainbow to the magical Land of Oz, continues to thrill audiences worldwide.<span><br/></span>
""";
